        {
            "title": "微軟自高位回落25%後  趁低吸納定快快走人？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"微軟自高位回落25%後 趁低吸納定快快走人？\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"643\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/D9mCXGcQT9mr3DDLj_g0Pw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/4a95f2c0-1e1a-11f1-96f7-6425b34a8d31\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">微軟自高位回落25%後 趁低吸納定快快走人？</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
